{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01Vyr6HeXgWTshX6o7md8k2b","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Vitest doesn't have `envFile` configuration, so it likely doesn't load `.env.local` automatically. Let me check if dotenv is used or if Vitest loads `.env` files.\n\nIn Vitest, by default it doesn't load `.env.local` files. Vite (which Vitest uses) does load `.env` and `.env.local` files, but since this is using `defineConfig` from `vitest/config` (not from `vite`), I need to check.\n\n\nActually, I'm realizing Vitest v1+ should support loading env files, but the real issue here is that `.env.local` has `CLICKHOUSE_PASSWORD` set to an empty string, and the test is using `process.env.CLICKHOUSE_PASSWORD ?? \"password\"` which would use the empty string instead of the fallback.\n\nThe eval confirms `.env.local` isn't being loaded, so `CLICKHOUSE_PASSWORD` is undefined and the test defaults to `\"password\"` instead of the empty string. The fix is probably to explicitly set the default to an empty string in the test since that's what the local server expects. I need to figure out whether Vitest is actually loading the `.env.local` file—if it's not, that explains why the default password isn't being picked up correctly. The real fix might be to add explicit `envFile` configuration to `vitest.config.ts` so the environment variables are properly loaded during tests. on the eval feedback, I need to fix the timestamp format in the identity module to match ClickHouse's expected format, and ensure the test environment loads the correct password from `.env.local`. There are also pre-existing test failures in the migration and ClickHouse integration tests that stem from the same password configuration issue. The real issue is that Vitest isn't loading `.env.local` automatically, even though the file exists with the password configuration. I need to either configure Vitest to load environment files or explicitly set the password in the vitest config itself.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1534,"cache_read_input_tokens":39806,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1534},"output_tokens":22,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"29f5e167-8f6c-43c0-81d3-b3219e5fab16","uuid":"c8aaafe1-4b0a-41e7-81a8-25d0f3330b9b"}
